<p><font color="#5A5AEF" size="3" face="Times New Roman"><b>NA BUKOMO BWA MUYA UJILA, MWINE KIDISHITU
UBWANYA&nbsp;DIFUKU NE DIFUKU KWIKALA NA BUMI BWA
 BUSHINDANGANI.</b></font></p>
<p><font face="Times New Roman">Po watambwile Yesti Kidishitu, Muya Ujila watwelele ne kwikala modi.
Muya Ujila upa Mwine Kidishitu yense bumi bubwaninine bwa
nsangaji ne bushindangani.</font></p>
<p><font face="Times New Roman">Bino bishima bya mukanda ukola bitulombola'mba:</font></p>
<p><font face="Times New Roman">1.&nbsp; Muya Ujila i Leza <b><font color="#5A5AEF">(Mingilo 5:3-5).</font></b><br>
2.&nbsp; Muya Ujila udi mu bumi bwa muntu yense upwile kutambula Yesu Kidishitu bu Mfumwandi&nbsp;<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b><font color="#5A5AEF">(1 Bene Kodinda&nbsp; 3:16; Bene Loma 8:9).&nbsp;</font></b>&nbsp;<br>
3.&nbsp; Muya Ujila witupa bukomo bwa bumi bwa bwine Kidishitu <b><font color="#5A5AEF">(Bene Ngalatea 5:22-23; Bene Loma 8).</font></b><br>
4.&nbsp; Muya Ujila witupa bukomo bwa kuleta bu kamonyi bwa Yesu Kidishitu <b><font color="#4044FF">(Mingilo
1:8)</font><font color="#2020B8">.</font></b><br>
5.&nbsp; Muya Ujila udi na bukomo kutabuka miuya yonso mikwabo <b><font color="#5A5AEF">(1 Yoano 4:14).</font></b></font></p>
<p><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Mukanda Ukola witulombola miswelo isatu ya bantu:</font></p>
    <p><b><font face="Times New Roman" color="#5A5AEF">(1) MUNTU WAMPIKWA YESU KIDISHITU</font></b></p>
    <p><font face="Times New Roman"> 
    <b> 
    Muya Ujila keudipo mu mutyima wa yewa katambwile po Yesu bu Mukudi wandi</b> <b><font color="#5A5AEF">(Bene Efisesa 1:13)</font></b></font></p>
<p><font face="Times New Roman">Mukanda Ukola umena'mba: <b>&quot;Ebiya kadi mutyima wa bu</b><b>muntu keusepelelapo bya&nbsp;Muya Ujila wa Leza, ehe,</b><b> </b><b>kebintu abyo i bilembakane kudi aye. Aye nandi ne</b><b>
</b><b>
mwakwibiyukila mpika, mwanda abyo biyukibwa konka</b><b> </b><b>ku Muya Ujila.&quot;</b>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<b><font color="#5A5AEF">(I Bene Kodinda 2:14)</font>
</b></font></p>
<p><font face="Times New Roman">Kifwatulo kino kilombola kinfwa kya muntu wampikwa Yesu</font></p>
