        </td>
        <td width="40" height="93">
        <p align="center"><font face="Times New Roman"><img border="0" src="images/chair.gif" width="24" height="44"></font></td>
        <td><b><font face="Times New Roman" color="#5A5AEF">=&nbsp; Lupona lwa bumi bwa muntu</font></b></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td width="40" height="19">
        <p align="center"><font face="Times New Roman"><img border="0" src="images/cross.gif" width="23" height="38"></font></td>
        <td><b><font face="Times New Roman" color="#5A5AEF">=&nbsp; Yesu Kidishitu</font></b></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
</div>
<p><font face="Times New Roman">1. Yesu udi panja pa bumi bwandi.<br>
2. Muntu udi pa lupona. Wendeja bumi bwandi aye mwine.<br>
3. Muntu unou ufvvaninwe kutambula Yesu Kidishitu bu Mukudi wandi.</font></p>
    <p><font face="Times New Roman"><br>
    <b><font color="#5A5AEF">(2) MWINE KIDISHITU MUYULWE MUYA UJILA</font></b> </font> </p>
    <p><font face="Times New Roman">
 Pa kyaba po tutambula Yesu Kidishitu bu Mukudi wetu, Muya Ujila wiya kwikala mo tudi <b><font color="#5A5AEF">(Bene Loma 8:9).</font></b> Kuyulwa Muya Ujila kushintulula'mba tubaitabija Yesu Kidishitu etwendeje ne kwitukunkuja. Tukulupile mu bukomo bwandi, ke mu bwetu po mhm. </font> </p>
<p><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;

Mukanda Ukola ushintulula bumi buyulwe ne Muya Ujila uno muswelo:</font></p>
<p><b><b><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="3">&#147;Ino kipa kya Muya Ujila i lusa, ne tusepo, ne ndoe, ne&nbsp;</font></font></b> <font face="Times New Roman"> <font size="3"> <b normal">kutukija mutyima,&nbsp;ne kanye, ne buyampe, ne bubine bine, ne kikokeji, ne kwifula, ino bino bidi&nbsp;namino</b> <b>kebidipo na kijila, nansha kimo&quot; </b><font color="#5A5AEF">(Bene Ngalatea 5:22-23)</font></font></font></b></p>
<p><b><font size="3">
<b normal">&quot;Ino banwe mukapewa bukomo bwa Muya Ujila</b> <b>ukemwila ko mudi,</b> <b>mukekala&nbsp;ba tumoni twami</b> <b>bakusapula mu Yelusalema, ne monso mu Yudea, ne</b> <b normal">mu
</b><b>Samadia, ne kulampe kwine kumfulo kwa ntanda&quot;.&nbsp; </b> <font color="#5A5AEF">(Mingilo&nbsp; 1:8)</font></font></b></p>
