        <td align="center"><font face="Times New Roman"><img border="0" src="images/law4.2x.gif" width="150" height="138"></font></td>
        <td>
        <p><b><font color="#5A5AEF" face="Times New Roman">Talai nanshi :</font></b></p>
        <p><b><font color="#5A5AEF" face="Times New Roman">1.Yesu Kidishitu udi mu mutyima mwa uno muntu.</font></b></p>
        <p><b><font color="#5A5AEF" face="Times New Roman">2. Yesu Kidishitu udi pa lupona lwa bumi bwandi. I aye umwendeja.</font></b></p>
        <p><b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#5A5AEF">&nbsp;</font><font color="#5A5AEF">3. Uno mwine Kidishitu udi na bumi bwa kwingidila Yesu.</font></font></b></p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
</div>
<p style="text-align:justify">
<font face="Times New Roman">Po tumupa Yesu Kidishitu bwendeji bwa bumi bwetu twikala ne kyaka kya kusangaja Leza, kya kutanga Mukanda Ukola ne kulombela. Tusangala kusapula Yesu ku bantu bakwabo ne kwibkunga ne bene kidishitu bakwabo. Bumi bwetu bukapa kipa kya Muya Ujila.</font></p>
<p><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;
Bino bintu bimweka bitye-bitye mwendela mafuku mu bumi bwa mwine kidishitu (1) Pa tama lukulupilo lwandi mudi Yesu mu bintu byonso bya bumi bwandi (2) ne mwendela bya tana mu bwine kidishitu bwandi. Mwine kidishitu muyulwe ne Muya Ujila ke mubwanininepo, mhm, inoko ukulupile'mba Leza wingila mu bumi bwandi.</font></p>
<p><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;Ekale mwine kidishitu kayudilwe na Muya Ujila, udi bu&nbsp;</font></p>
<p><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#4044FF">(3) MWINE KIDISHITU WA BUNGITU</font></b> </font></p>
    <p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman"> 
Mwine kidishitu wa bungitu i mupyasakene enka mu bisangaja yandi ngitu kutabukako bisaka Leza. Mwine kidishitu wa bungitu udingakene pamo nka na mwana wa lukeke ulonga mwasakila, udi monka nka bwa muntu mwine ntanda wakukulupila mu bukomo bwa aye mwine amba amone bumi bwa bwine kidishitu.</font>
    </p>
<p><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;Mukanda Ukola<b> </b>ulombola mwine kidishitu wa bungitu uno muswelo:</font></p>
<p><font face="Times New Roman"><b>&#147;Ebiya,</b><b normal; mso-tab-count: 1; font-size: 12.0pt; 10.0pt"> </b><b>banwe bana</b><b normal; mso-tab-count: 1; font-size: 12.0pt; 10.0pt"> </b><b>betu, </b><b>ami</b> <b>nkiyukilepo</b> 
 <b>kwimwisambila pamo na boba ba&nbsp;ku Muya Ujila, ehe,</b> 
 <b>poso pamo na boba ba ku bungitu, ke pamo na twana twa
</b><b normal">lukeke mudi Kidishitu kadi. nemutomeja mabele,</b> <b>kwimudisha mwita mpika, ke&nbsp;mwi-bantu kemwayukileo, </b><b normal">ne pano pene kemuyukileo mhm. Pa mwanda o mukidi ba
ku bungitu monka, lelo byo mukidi ne kilokoloko, ne</b><b> </b><b>
lupata umbukata mwenu, ke&nbsp;mudipo ba ku bungitu, ne kunangila mu muswelo wa bu muntu, a?&quot;
<font color="#4044FF">(1 Bene Kodinda 3:1-3)</font>
</b></font></p>
<p><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Bumi bwa mwine Kidishitu wa bungitu budi na biyukeno bino</b><b>:</b></font></p>
