    <p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman"><i>Pa bano bantu basatu, usaka wikale bwa ani le?<br>
    </i>Twalamukanga ketudi bene Kidishitu pa lwitabijo lwetu mudi yesu Kidishitu bu Mupandiji. Mo monka, tuyulwa Muya Ujila pa lwitabijo.</font></p>
    <center>

    <p align="center"><b><font color="#4044FF" face="Times New Roman">UBWANYA&nbsp; KUYULWA&nbsp; MUYA&nbsp; UJILA&nbsp; ENKA&nbsp; PANO&nbsp; PONKA</font></b>
