    <center>

    <p align="center"><b><font color="#4044FF" face="Times New Roman">MUSONGANYA WANDI, MULAO WANDI</font></b>
</p>
</center>    
    <p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman">Leza ukakuyuja Muya Ujila (kukwendeja ne kukupa bukorno) shi umukulupile. Ubwanya kuyuka bu bine-bine mwanda Mukanda Ukola unena'niba:</font>
</p>
    <p></b><font face="Times New Roman"><b normal">ne lupoto</b><b>-</b><b>poto poso muyu1,wc&nbsp;enka Muya Ujila&quot;.</b> <b><font color="#4044FF">(Bene Efisesa 5:18)</font></b></font></p>
    <p><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Leza usaka'mba bene Kidishi bonso bayulwc Muya Ujila-Esprit.</b></font></p>
    <p><font face="Times New Roman"><i>&quot;Mulao wandi., </i><b>&quot;Ino buno namino bo bukankamane botudi nabo</b><b> </b><b>mudi aye, twa'mba&nbsp;wivwanc tulombe kintu, shi kika, shi kika,</b><b> </b><b>monka muswidile mutyima wandi, nankyo&nbsp;witwivwana. Kadi, shi tuyukile'mba witwivwananga, ne byonso byo tulomba,</b><b> </b><b>nankyo&nbsp;tubayuka'mba ke tudi kala nabyo </b><b>b</b><b>yak</b><b>ul</b><b>omba byo twamulombele&#148;</b> <b><font color="#4044FF">(1 Yoano 5:14-15)</font></b></font></p>
    <p><font face="Times New Roman">Bidi Mukanda Ukola witusonganya kuyulwa Muya Ujila, tubayuka'niba i kiswamutyima kya Leza aye kulongela monka. Yuka bine bine&#146;mba Leza ukakuyuja na Muya wandi Ujila shi umulomba ne kukulupila. I mulaye kulondolola ku milonibelo &nbsp;yetu mwendela kyandi kiswa-mutyinia.</font></p>
    <p align="center"><b><font color="#4044FF" face="Times New Roman">TUYULWA MUYA UJILA PA LWITABIJO</font></b></p>
    <p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman">Milombelo i dishinda dilonibola lwitabijo lobe. Tala nanshi niofwaninue kulombela:</font></p>
    <p align="left"><b><font face="Times New Roman">&quot;MFUMWETU YESU, NKUSAKA, NAYUKA'MBA NA ENDEJE BUMI BWAMI AMI MWINE NENKI NALUBILE KUMESO OBE. NEJIBA KU BUBI BUNO NE KUKULUPILA ENKA MODI. NAKUFWIJA PA KUNDEKELA MAMBO PA LUFU LOBE PA MUSALABU. MFUMWETU, NDYUJE NA MLUYA UJILA OBE MWENDELA MUSONGANYA OBE NE MULAO OBE. UBAFUKO PA KUNDYUJA MUYA UJILA NE PA KUJOKELA PA BWENDEJI BWA BUMI BWAMI. AMINA&quot;.</font></b></p>
    <p style="text-align:justify" <font face="Times New Roman">Lelo uswile kunangila mu bukoino ne kukunkujibwa na Muya Ujila? Shi i arno, ubwanya kulomba uno muswelo pano pano ponka.</font></p>
    <p align="center"><b><font color="#4044FF" face="Times New Roman">MWA KUYUKILA'MBA WIMUYULWE NA MUYA UJILA</font></b></p>
    <p><font face="Times New Roman" Lelo wadi ubalombe Leza akuyuje ne Muya Ujila?<br>
    Lelo uyukile'mba pano wi muyulwc na Muya Ujila?<br>
    Ubwanya kwi kiyuka pa niwanda wa <i style="mso-bidi-font-style:normal">musonganya wandi </i><font color="#4044FF"><b>(Bene Efisesa 5:18)</b> </font>ne wa <i style="mso-bidi-font-style:normal">mulao wandi&nbsp;<font color="#4044FF"><b>(1 </b></font></i><font color="#4044FF"><b>Yoafio 5:14-15)</b></font>. Kukekala mafuku okevwana'mba udi kubwipi na Leza. Mafuku makwabo ukevwana'mba udi kulampe na Leza. Yuka'mba mlangwe ishintanga mwendela byaba byotanwaruo. Nansha inankyo fwija tu Leza ne kadi kokikulupila mu milangwc yobe ishinta. Kidupila mu Mwanda wandi, ke muruilangwc yobe po.</font></p>
    <p><b><font face="Times New Roman">Ubwanya kujingulula kisanso ne lulekelo lwa Leza ku dyuba-ku dyuba.</font></b></p>
    <p><font face="Times New Roman">Muya Ujila ukakulornbola nycke bifwaninwc kushinta mu bobe bunii, po kekala wenda na Mfumwetu ne ku musangaja. Pa ka kufikila kufityija Leza mutyima (mu binenwa, mu mil angwe, nausha mu bilongwa), mufwijetu pangala pa lulekelo iwandi lo watarnbwile pa kupopwa kwa Yesti Kidishitu pa musalabu. Kulupila mu kisanso kyaudi ne mu lulekelo Iwandi; eudelela kunanga nandi.</font></p>
    <p align="center"><b><font color="#4044FF" face="Times New Roman">KWIKALA MU KITATYI KYONSO MUYULWE MUYA UJILA</font></b></p>
    <p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman">Muya Ujila kalekelelapo nansha dimo mwine kidishitu. Nanshi kifwaninwe kumidekela bwendeji bwa bumi bobe difiiku dyouso. Bibwanika kushikata monka pa lupona kwa bumi bobe polonga bubi, shi kukokelepo Leza mu mifwatakanyo yobe, mu binenwa byobe nausha mu milangwc mine. Shi ubalonga kino, naushi <i style="mso-bidi-font-style:
normal">esa mu muya ujila.</i></font></p>
    <p align="center"><b><font face="Times New Roman">Kwesa mu muya ujila i namani?</font></b></p>
    <p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman">Ngitu ilupula muya mubi pa kwesa, kadi pa kukoka muya mupya nao wapingakana muya mubi wadi ubatambe. Mo monka, kwesa mu Muya Ujila kuka kukwasha kwijiba bubi bobe ne kuiyulwa monka na Muya Ujfla wa Leza.</font></p>
    <p><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#4044FF">(1 Yoano 1:9)</font>. Mufwijeko pa kulekelwa kwa mambo obe. Vundamuina bubi bobe.</font></p>
    <p style="tab-stops:17.9pt"><font face="Times New Roman" &nbsp;<b>2. <b>Lomba Yesu ajokele monka pa lupona </b><b normal; font-size: 12.0pt; 10.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">l</b><b>wa bumi bobe </b><b><font color="#4044FF">(Bene Lonia 6:13)</font></b> <b>Wipane kudi Muya </b><b>Ujila</b> <b>ne ke mulomba akuyuje monka.
    Vuluka <i style="mso-bidi-font-style:normal">musonganya wandi </i>mu <font color="#4044FF">Bene Efisesa 5:18</font> </b> <i style="mso-bidi-font-style:normal">ne Mulao </i>mu&nbsp;<b><font color="#4044FF">1 Yoano 5:14-15.</font></b></font></p>
    <p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman">Esa mu Muya Ujila kyaba kyonso ki kulombola Muya, Ujila bubi modi, ne ukekala na bumi bwa sangaji ne bwa bushindaganyi bu tumbija Leza. Lekela Muya Ujiba endelele kwendeja bumi bobe kitatyi ne kitatyi.</font></p>
    <p align="center"><b><font color="#4044FF" face="Times New Roman">KWIKALA NYEKE MU KUYULWA NA MUYA UJILA</font></b></p>
    <p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Muleke Yesu Kidishitu akwendeje nyeke mu bintu byonso bya mu bumi bobe:</b></font></p>
    <p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman">Bitatyi byobe bya kwisangaja, ningilo yobc, bituntwa byobc, mwikadilo wa kisaka kyobe ne balunda, ne bekadi nobc. Muleke Yesu ekale na bumi bwandi modi mu kyaba kyonso. Shi wikele mudi Yesu Kidishitu, Leza ukendelela kwalamuna bumi bobe. Shi upane bwendeji bwa bumi bobe kudi Muya Ujila:</font></p>
    <p><font face="Times New Roman" &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.&nbsp; Bumi bobe bukalombola bine bine kipa kya Muya Ujila <b><font color="#4044FF">(Bene Ngalatea 5:22-23).</font></b><br>
    2. Milombelo yobe ikekala ne buluji <b><font color="#4044FF">(Yakoba 5:16).</font></b><br>
    3. Ukayukidija bininge kwivwanija Mukanda Ukola <b><font color="#4044FF">(2 Teruote 3:16-17)</font></b><br>
    4. Ukatambula bukomo bwa Leza bwa kuleta bu Kamoni <b><font color="#4044FF">(Mingilo 1:8).</font></b><br>
    5. Ukatambula bukonio bwa Leza bwa kushinda bitompibwa ne bubi bwine. <b><font color="#4044FF">(1 Bene Kodinda 10:13).</font></b></font></p>
    <p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman">Kulupila mudi Leza ne mu yandi nilao idi mu Mukanda Ukola. Mwine kidishitu wikala na bumi buyulwe na Muya Ujila enka pa Iwitabijo.</font></p>
    <p align="center"><b><font color="#4044FF" face="Times New Roman">BUMO BWA BWINE KIDISHITU</font></b></p>
    <font face="Times New Roman" Shi bibanze bya nkuni bidi pamo mu mudilo, bitema bininge. Inoko shi abebisansanya, mudilo wa alula kiibula. Mo nonka, bikakukomena kumona bumi bwa bwine kidishitu bunka bobe. Ibiyampe kodi kwibunga na bantu bakwabo batambwile Yesu Kidishitu bu Mfumwabo ne bu wabo Mukudi.</font>
    <p><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Pwila mu kipwilo mo bakulupile'mba Mukanda Ukola i wa bine­bine ne mo batota Yesu Kidishitu. </b><b><font color="#4044FF">(Babebelu 10:25)</font></b></font></p>
    <p><font face="Times New Roman">Ma vese alembelwc atanwa mu &quot;Myanda Miyampe ku bonso&quot;</font></p>
    <p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman">Shi ka dibuku kano kaba kukwasha, tangako na muntu mukwabo.</font></p>
    <font face="Times New Roman" Shi usaka kuyuka biyampe motwingidila, lemba ku bibadiko bya mobo a mingilo yetu:</font>
    <p><font face="Times New Roman" B.P. 7721, Kinshasa I, Zalre<br>
    B.P. 1691, Shaba, Lubumbashi</font></p>
    <p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman">Ufwaninwe kwingidila ka dibuku. kanoka, inoko pakusaka kulama ne kutyinyija konakanya bilembwa bya ka dibuku kano, kwikalemba kipindi, nansha konso katuntulu abe mwine ibikankajibwe pakubulwa lupusa lwa mwimaniji wa Campus pour Christ. Ka buku i kalembwe na William R. Bright. Copyright: Campus pour Christ.</font></p>
